Deploy a cover;
Increase the Attack of allies within a circular range by $1 for $2. (Effect applies only while within range)
The cover additionally inherits $3 Kirino's HP.

Deal $1 damage to one enemy;
Reduce target Defense by $2 for $3;
If the enemy has Light armor, reduce their Defense by $4 for $5.
